info: The proposed Project will address critical urban development issues of Viet Tri, Hung Yen, and Dong Dang in northern Viet Nam along the North-South economic corridor (NSEC), in contributing to the transformation of the NSEC from transport corridor into full-fledged economic corridor and in complementing Hanoi as alternative growth centers.
name: COMPRE SOCIO-ECO URBAN DEV'L PROJ N VIET TRI, HUNG YEN, &DONG DAN
